OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1774887078
OL,3,CFarmers oppose plans to re-introduce
OL,4,Csea eagles
OL,6,FFarmers have expressed their
OL,7,Fopposition to plans to re-introduce
OL,8,Fthe sea eagle to Cumbria.
OL,10,FSea eagles, also known as white-tailed
OL,11,Feagles, are the largest bird of prey
OL,12,Fin the United Kingdom.
OL,14,FThey became extinct in the UK in the
OL,15,Fearly 20th Century, according to the
OL,16,FRoyal Society for the Protection of
OL,17,FBirds, but were reintroduced in
OL,18,FScotland in 1975 and on the Isle of
OL,19,FWight in 2019.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/6
