OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1774887078
OL,3,CFarmers oppose plans to re-introduce
OL,4,Csea eagles
OL,6,FThe Lifescape Project charity says
OL,7,FCumbria would provide a suitable
OL,8,Fhabitat for the birds, and that there
OL,9,Fwould be plenty of natural food for
OL,10,Fthe eagles.
OL,12,FDr Deborah Brady from Lifescape told
OL,13,FITV Border: "White-tailed eagles
OL,14,Fmainly feed on fish and waterbirds,
OL,15,Fand some scavenging. From Scotland we
OL,16,Fknow there are worries about direct
OL,17,Flivestock predation.
OL,19,F"We've heard directly from 285 farmers
OL,20,Fand landowners about concerns that
OL,21,Fthere may be livestock predation.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1774887078
OL,3,CFarmers oppose plans to re-introduce
OL,4,Csea eagles
OL,6,F"This has not happened in other areas
OL,7,Fwhere the white-tailed eagle has been
OL,8,Fre-introduced."
OL,10,FOn the reasons behind re-introducing
OL,11,Fthis type of bird, Dr Brady said: "We
OL,12,Ftend to focus on species that need a
OL,13,Fhelping hand to come back.
OL,15,F"We are in a biodiversity crisis, and
OL,16,Fwe're not doing great in the UK.
OL,18,F"(On) bringing eagles back to Cumbria,
OL,19,Fover the last five years we've looked
OL,20,Fat whether it would work biologically
OL,21,Fand practically.
OL,26,@zD@BpmzD@Epn
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/6
