PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1774887078
OL,3,CFarmers oppose plans to re-introduce
OL,4,Csea eagles
OL,6,F"We've taken the conversation to
OL,7,Fpeople in Cumbria, and we know there's
OL,8,Fbroad support of 78%."
